description: A non-partisan US watchdog agency says the White House block on congressional aid was illegal.
title: White House 'broke law' by withholding Ukraine aid, says watchdog
title_page: White House 'broke law' by withholding Ukraine aid, says watchdog - BBC News
maintext: Mr Trump has said he does not know Mr Parnas. Referring to photos of himself with Mr Parnas and another Giuliani associate, he said: "It's possible I have a picture with them because I have a picture with everybody."
